      • DICOMVolume

        public DICOMVolume()
        This default constructor should not be used. If you use this method, it gonna print some information into the console and call System.exit(1).

      • DICOMVolume

        public DICOMVolume(java.lang.String path)
        This constructor searching in the given path for files. In this folder there should only be one type of images. If the names of the images don't end with a known ending, the images handled as a IMA image.
        Parameters:
        path - The Location, of the Dicom Volume
